    item: "buttons",
    type: "secondary-solid"
  }) }}

  <h3>When to use a secondary button</h3>
  <p>Use a secondary button either:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>for secondary actions on a page</li>
    <li>when an action needs less prominence, for example because it is optional</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Pages with too many calls to action make it hard for users to know what to do next. Before adding lots of secondary buttons, try to simplify the page or break the content down across multiple pages.</p>
